name: Patrol loop 631152047. All systems nominal.
description: The deep space relay station near Tau Centauri hasn’t been visited in thousands of years. It has been cut off from its surrounding universe by a nova - there is no available information about nearby life forms. Its computer, however, is still performing routine maintenance, including onboard dataset maintenance. Currently, for the past 600 years, it has developed an affection towards specific data, some musical works by a human composer from the pre-FTL years, and so it adjusts the station’s window apertures to play his music to the vegetation on deck.
